(1) There shall be established an Hotels Board , which shall consist of— (a) a Chairman and a Vice-Chairman ; (b) an Advocate of the High Court for Zambia; (c) a health inspector; (d) a member of the Hotels and Catering Association of Zambia; (e) a member of the Hotels and Catering Workers' Union of Zambia; and (f) not more than three other members.
